title: silkonmenina
author: silkonmenina
content: The Antminer S19 Pro+ Hydro is Bitmain’s first ever liquid cooled S19 ASIC miner, with an efficiency rating of 27.5 J/TH and a power consumption of 5445W. Hydro-cooling technology makes this miner more powerful and more efficient than the base S19 model, with a hashrate of 188 TH/s.AlgorithmSHA-256NetworkEthernetVoltage12VChip-Fan(s)4Noise level26dbTemperature5 - 40°CHumidity5 - 95 %Size410x196x209mmWeight17500gPM : +1(765)279-7770
